@exercises DAG (DAG)
@surface   DAG.compile, DAG.targetTracks, DAG.validate

# Intent
  (none)

# Helpers
  @fn source(id, guid)  @ 4-9
  @fn fx(id, opts)  @ 11-20
  @fn master(opts)  @ 22-27
  @fn mk(nodes, edges)  @ 29-34
  @fn twoSourceChain(splitB)  @ 38-50
      -- s1 -> a -> b -> master, s2 -> master. Two sources, so master's class
      -- differs from the {s1} chain: marking b evicts it cleanly.
